platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: Open the door to a new world
自然のバランスを修復する。

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Kenshō is a delightful adventure, packed with brain-bending challenges. It routinely twists its rules in clever ways to make every sliding tile puzzle feel distinct. Stunning graphics, a wonderful soundtrack, and a surprisingly engaging story make this both a rewarding emotional journey and a must-play for puzzle fans.
